column5: I'd like to receive text message reminders and updates about Equip classes.
column6: Do you have any comments or questions about the class before it starts?

Family - my spouse judges them non stop - very hard for me but he feels very justified in his ways.   He says he’s forgiven them for things they have done to me but holds on to his judgement for them.   Please keep this confidential he is attending the class with me.  I don’t bother telling him things anymore because I have to hear about how awful they are - very hard.  None of us are perfect and his comments don’t help me feel supported -
